value: 2273 - Carpets and Rugs Summary > MILLIKEN (AUSTRALIA) PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover carpets and rugs. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. MILLIKEN (AUSTRALIA) PTY LTD is headquartered in Northmead, New South Wales. It is headed by director & general manager James Robert Mccallum. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $36.74 million. Its net loss totalled $4.09 million. MILLIKEN (AUSTRALIA) PTY LTD forms part of the manufacturing industry sector. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
